Source: bob
Section: science
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Biometrics Group <biometric@idiap.ch>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7.0.50), quilt, cmake, python, pkg-config, liblapack-dev, libatlas-base-dev, libblitz1-dev, libboost-all-dev, libhdf5-serial-dev, libvl-dev, doxygen, graphviz
