Package: bob
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: hdf5-tools, h5utils
Suggests: libhdf5-doc
Description: Python/C++ Framework for Machine Learning and Signal Processing
 Bob is a signal-processing and machine learning framework developed at the
 Idiap Research Institute, Switzerland. The framework is written in a mix of
 Python and C++ and is designed to be both efficient and to reduce development
 time.
 .
 This package provides the C++ runtime libraries.

